   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.560", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir m\u00fcssen das grundgesetzlich regeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.480", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit diese einfachgesetzlichen Regelungen nicht irgendwann einfachgesetzlich au\u00dfer Kraft gesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.320", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.960", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen auch keine Angst haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.360", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn unser Gesetzentwurf durchgeht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.960", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen niemandem verbieten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.760", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
